  "body": "# Problem\n\nAfter a transaction has been paid and user re-login and goes to the chat with the contact he paid tribute to, the value of the tribute and the personalized message are gone.\n\n## Implementation\n\nCurrently tribute amount and personalized message are not persisted and just fetched from the manifest which is necessary to make sure it is as up to date as possible. However once the tribute has been paid it could be saved. The amount paid is redundant with the transaction message though.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- after tribute is paid and users re-login, the tribute amount and personalized message are visible (and they have been persisted from the manifest state when the tribute was paid)\n\nOR\n\n- a different view is shown once the tribute is paid @errorists",
